{"tid":784036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港故事： 粗口月餅爆紅狂收定單","createTime":"2018-08-18T05:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T07:37:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"662c3d179c085ee650bb644ca1d9e1cdc938ad89","tid":784036,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:02:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180818/20479188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F20479188&d=CdBojDA0%2B%2FR19bAFQBYf8gIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=731ba852\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F20479188&h=a6b4bda9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180818/20479188</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月18日 <br />\n<br />\n港故事：<br />\n粗口月餅爆紅狂收定單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180818/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180818%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=5fab90ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■粗口月餅有六款，包括流行潮語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180818/large/a1102b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180818%2Flarge%2Fa1102b.gif&h=d124974d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■舊式月餅模具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前，餅店的月餅由孫母人手製作，每年銷量約8,000個，主要售予慈善機構及老人中心，Naomi坦言，傳統月餅形象太老，已被年輕人遺忘。兩年前，餅店推出紫薯及綠茶豆沙餡月餅，甜度大減，更加健康。今年，創意無限的Naomi更推出粗口月餅，沒料到於網上爆紅，更收到大量定單。<br />\n<br />\nNaomi從櫃子一角找出一批木造月餅模，那些年，中秋前夕，工場漫天木頭碰撞聲，某些更已破損，「雙黃個模最殘，因為受歡迎，用得多嘛！」如今的月餅模都改用塑膠造的，成本只需約50元，只是木模的十分一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加入潮語反應好<br />\n<br />\n「香港人壓力真係大！」Naomi笑言，粗口月餅原本送給朋友，因此只有「x你咩，哈哈！」一款，豈料放上網後，引來熱烈迴響，大批客人有意訂購，因此Naomi再設計5款潮語月餅，包括：「心好累x街」、「打x你寶寶」、「好x正呀喂」，每個售$38。如此破格的出品，孫母有否阻止？「冇喎，做到生意就得啦！」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港故事：餅女爆粗　老店逢春"},{"pid":"388fad78eb73a9068e3a4e0c31a6917c65f4dc61","tid":784036,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"Creative<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a8e0df56c26cea709a475fb4d3ab51bb0a1ee4","tid":784036,"uid":3405,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n印蝗語"},{"pid":"c968f99acf9a7055f3f899383d6ac90c07a42757","tid":784036,"uid":189048,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17b9e71d396f0aa72c0933195d7b7ae7626d3455","tid":784036,"uid":174013,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"心好累 x街<br />\n癡膠線親親<br />\n打 x你寶寶<br />\n<br />\n支那蝗語扮港產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74064f296b1c35a59a5b8d0815c2c3cf73734a2","tid":784036,"uid":52234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"17b9e71d396f0aa72c0933195d7b7ae7626d3455","tid":784036,"uid":174013,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"心好累 x街<br />\n癡膠線親親<br />\n打 x你寶寶<br />\n<br />\n支那蝗語扮港產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"想做支那人生意 香港人點會用呢啲字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b574c6d1115742c6b453103273bd96e413a752","tid":784036,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a1e92615a5b3bb03d485e796f24541bdfda706d","tid":784036,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:33:53.000Z","msg":"蝗語扮本土<img src